metadata.name: The Call - Abstract Landscape Oil Painting
metadata.description:
The Call is a heavily textured abstract oil painting by artist Ishrath Humairah in impressionist style where you can see faint semblance of deeply wooded forests, with its pristine blue water-bodies and abundant flora, blending into one another. 

Title: The Call
Medium: Oil on Canvas - Texture artwork
Size: 45 x 33 inches

The artwork's digital image is available as 1/1 NFT where you get high quality digital image of the original artwork for personal use. 

For purchasing the original tangible/physical artwork, please reach out to the artist. 

Thank you.
